caption: Finally checked this one off my bucket list. After an exhausting hike with 2000 vertical meters we arrived at the first of three Watzmann peaks and the views couldn’t have been better. #watzmann

Just came back home from Skjervøy, Norway, where I experienced one of the most amazing moments ever.
Together with @articaadventures & @beyer_photo I searched for the killer whale in the Lyngen Fjords.
On our last day in the water we found an orca pod hunting for herrings. Swimming with these animals up close was an unforgettable experience.

Commemorating World Photography Day with a selection of my favorite #shotoniphone captures from the last two years. My photography journey began with an iPod at age 12, and still, 11 years later, the camera that I always have with me is the iPhone. Here's to the memories we’ve captured and the stories still waiting to be told. Happy World Photography Day! #worldphotographyday
